lyrics:
I'm on a mission, fueled by ambition
Every obstacle I face, I turn into ammunition
They try to bring me down, but I rise above
I'm unstoppable, fueled by love

[Chorus]
Motivation, determination, that's the key
No matter what they say, I'll always believe
In myself, in my dreams, in my destiny
I'm Kanye West, and I'm living my legacy

[Verse 2]
I'm a visionary, a true revolutionary
Breaking barriers, setting new boundaries
I refuse to be confined by society's norms
I'm breaking down walls, blowing up the norms
